---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Affiliate Disclosure"
  description="How Australian Home Collective handles affiliate links."
>
  <header class="page-intro">
    <div class="narrow">
      <p class="eyebrow">Disclosure</p>
      <h1>Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        Some pages on Australian Home Collective may contain affiliate links.
      </p>
    </div>
  </header>
  <section class="content narrow">
    <p>
      If you buy through an affiliate link, Australian Home Collective may earn a commission.
      This should not cost you extra.
    </p>

    <h2>How this affects guides</h2>
    <p>
      Affiliate relationships should not change the practical purpose of the guides. We aim to
      help readers understand product types, features, storage needs and buying considerations
      before they choose what suits their home.
    </p>

    <h2>Reader choice</h2>
    <p>
      You are never required to use our links. Before buying, check the retailer's current
      product information, price, delivery details, returns policy and suitability for your
      household.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
